ZH: 在生活中，我们常常会在不甯危机的时刻揭竿而起。
EN: In life, we often rise up in the face of unexpected crises.

ZH: 当团队遇到困难时，大家都会团结一致，揭竿而起。
EN: When a team faces challenges, everyone will unite and rise up together.

ZH: 这个国家在面临危机时，人民总是能够揭竿而起。
EN: The people in this country always manage to rise up in times of crisis.

ZH: 当人们受到不公正对待时，他们会揭竿而起，为自己的权益而战。
EN: When people are treated unfairly, they will rise up and fight for their rights.

ZH: 高效的领导总能在必要时揭竿而起，为团队带来胜利。
EN: Effective leaders are always able to rise up when necessary and bring victory to the team.

ZH: 古代中国人在面对外敌入侵时，总能揭竿而起，捍卫祖国。
EN: Ancient Chinese people were always able to rise up to defend their homeland against foreign invaders.

ZH: 当环境遭到破坏时，人们应该揭竿而起，保护大自然。
EN: When the environment is being destroyed, people should rise up to protect nature.

ZH: 那个独裁政权一旦被推翻，人民就会揭竿而起，迎接自由的到来。
EN: Once the authoritarian regime is overthrown, the people will rise up and welcome the arrival of freedom.

ZH: 当家里发生火灾时，我们必须立刻揭竿而起，保护自己和家人。
EN: When a fire breaks out at home, we must immediately rise up to protect ourselves and our family.

ZH: 在面对经济危机时，企业要能够揭竿而起，找到新的发展方向。
EN: When facing an economic crisis, companies must be able to rise up and find new directions for development.

ZH: 孩子们被排挤在学校里，他们必须团结起来，揭竿而起。
EN: When children are excluded in school, they must unite and rise up together.

ZH: 当社区遭受破坏时，居民需要揭竿而起，维护自己的家园。
EN: When the community is being destroyed, residents need to rise up to protect their homeland.

ZH: 当干部腐败时，人民应该揭竿而起，捍卫廉洁政治。
EN: When officials are corrupt, the people should rise up to defend clean politics.

ZH: 在遭受欺凌时，受害者应该揭竿而起，寻求帮助。
EN: When facing bullying, victims should rise up and seek help.

ZH: 当处于生活困境时，我们不能束手就擒，而是要揭竿而起，寻找解决办法。
EN: When in a difficult situation in life, we should not give up but rise up and find solutions.

ZH: 在工作中遇到挑战时，我们应该揭竿而起，勇敢地面对问题。
EN: When facing challenges at work, we should rise up and bravely confront the issues.

ZH: 当有人遭受不公正待遇时，我们必须揭竿而起，支持他们。
EN: When someone is treated unjustly, we must rise up and support them.

ZH: 面对疫情的爆发，全国人民必须团结一致，揭竿而起。
EN: In the face of the outbreak of the epidemic, the people nationwide must unite and rise up together.

ZH: 当自由受到威胁时，人们应该揭竿而起，维护自己的权利。
EN: When freedom is threatened, people should rise up to defend their rights.
